quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,"wlqd khalaqna adam min tin yabis 'iidha nuqir ealayh sume lah swt, whdha altiyn alyabs min tin 'aswad mtghyir lwnh wryhh; min tul mkthh"
  15,27,"wkhlqna 'aba aljn, wahu 'iiblis min qabl khalaq adam min naar shadidat alhararat la dukhan lha"
  15,28,"wadhkr -ayha alnby- hin qal rabuk llmlaykt: 'iiniy khaliq 'insanana min tin yabs, whdha altiyn alyabs min tin 'aswad mtghyir allwn"
  15,29,"f'idha swwayth wakmlt suratih wanafakht fih alrwh, fkhurru lah sajidin sjwd tahiatan wtkrym, la sjwd ebadt"
  15,30,"fsjd almalayikat kuluhum 'ajmaeun kama 'amrihim rabihim lam ymtne minhum ahd, lkn 'iiblis aimtanae 'ana yasjud liadam mae almalayikat alsajdyn"
  15,31,"fsjd almalayikat kuluhum 'ajmaeun kama 'amrihim rabihim lam ymtne minhum ahd, lkn 'iiblis aimtanae 'ana yasjud liadam mae almalayikat alsajdyn"
  15,32,"qal allah l'iblys: ma lak 'alaa tasjud mae almlayk?"
  15,33,"qal 'iiblis mzhrana kibrah whsdh: la ylyq bi 'ana asjd li'iinsan 'awjdtah min tin yabis kan tynana 'aswad mtghyrana"
  15,34,"qal allah taealaa lh: fakhruj min aljnt, fa'iinak mtrwd min kuli khyr, wa'iina ealayk allaenat walbed min rahmati 'iilaa yawm yubeath alnaas llhsab waljza'"
  15,35,"qal allah taealaa lh: fakhruj min aljnt, fa'iinak mtrwd min kuli khyr, wa'iina ealayk allaenat walbed min rahmati 'iilaa yawm yubeath alnaas llhsab waljza'"
  15,36,"qal 'iblys: rabi akhkhirny fi aldunya 'iilaa alyawm aldhy tabeath fih ebadk, wahu yawm alqyamt"
  15,37,"qal allah lh: fa'iinak mmn akhkhart hlakhm 'iilaa alyawm aldhy yamut fih kl alkhalq baed alnfkht alawla, la 'iilaa yawm albeth, wa'iinama 'ujyb 'iilaa dhlk astdrajana lah w'imhala wftnt llthqlyn"
  15,38,"qal allah lh: fa'iinak mmn akhkhart hlakhm 'iilaa alyawm aldhy yamut fih kl alkhalq baed alnfkht alawla, la 'iilaa yawm albeth, wa'iinama 'ujyb 'iilaa dhlk astdrajana lah w'imhala wftnt llthqlyn"
  15,39,"qal 'iblys: rbb bsbb ma 'aghwaytani wadlltny lahssinann ldhryt adam measyk fi alard, wala'udilanahum 'ajmaein ean tariq alhda، 'iilaa eibadak aladhin hdythm fakhlsu lak alebadt whdk dun sayr khlqk"
  15,40,"qal 'iblys: rbb bsbb ma 'aghwaytani wadlltny lahssinann ldhryt adam measyk fi alard, wala'udilanahum 'ajmaein ean tariq alhda، 'iilaa eibadak aladhin hdythm fakhlsu lak alebadt whdk dun sayr khlqk"
  15,41,"qal allh: hdha tariq mustaqim metdl mwsl 'ily wa'iilaa dar kramty. 'iina eibadi aladhin akhlsu li la 'ajaeal lak sltanana ealaa qulubuhum tdlluhm bih ean alsirat almstqym, lkn sltank ealaa man atabaeak min aldaaliyn almushrikin aladhin raduu bwlaytk wtaetk badalaan min taety"
  15,42,"qal allh: hdha tariq mustaqim metdl mwsl 'ily wa'iilaa dar kramty. 'iina eibadi aladhin akhlsu li la 'ajaeal lak sltanana ealaa qulubuhum tdlluhm bih ean alsirat almstqym, lkn sltank ealaa man atabaeak min aldaaliyn almushrikin aladhin raduu bwlaytk wtaetk badalaan min taety"
  15,43,"wa'iin alnaar alshadidat lamwed 'iiblis watbaeh ajmeyn, laha sabeat 'abwab kuli bab 'asfal min alakhr, likuli bab min 'atbae 'iiblis qism wnsyb bhsb aemalhm"
  15,44,"w'in alnaar alshadidat lamwed 'iiblis watbaeh ajmeyn, laha sabeat 'abwab kuli bab 'asfal min alakhr, likuli bab min 'atbae 'iiblis qism wnsyb bhsb aemalhm"